464
00:29:33,355 --> 00:29:35,440
Sabias que ias ter uma noite dura.

465
00:29:37,109 --> 00:29:40,529
Quando tens o Ben Wallace,
o Stephen Jackson, o Ron Artest,

466
00:29:40,612 --> 00:29:43,282
